@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using PrivateLibrary.Data.Models
@inject SignInManager<ApplicationUser> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<ApplicationUser> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/Index" title="Manage">Здравей, @User.Identity?.Name!</a>
        </li>
        @if (User?.IsInRole("Reader") ?? false)
        {
           <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-action="TakenBooks" asp-controller="Account" asp-route-readerId="@UserManager.GetUserId(User)">Взети книги</a>
           </li> 
        }
        <li class="nav-item">
            <form class="form-inline" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Action("Index", "Home", new { area = "" })">
                <button type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-dark">Излизане</button>
            </form>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-action="RegisterReader" asp-controller="Account">Регистрация</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-action="Login" asp-controller="Account">Вход</a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>
